dct_title_s: Farm map of Hillsboro', Somerset Co. N.J.
dct_description_sm: "Entered according to Act of Congress, in the year 1860, by Matthew Hughes ... " Includes vignettes of buildings, list of subscribers and table of distances between villages. Shows names of property owners and number of acres owned. Wall map.
dct_publisher_sm: Phila. : Printed by T.S. Wagner, 38 Hudson St. , 1860 (Philada. : Lith. of Friend & Aub).
